    {
      "text": "Harley's Humongous Adventure is a 1993 platform video game developed by Visual Concepts for the Super Nintendo Entertainment System. It was originally funded by publisher Electronic Arts, but eventually published by Hi Tech Expressions.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "wikipedia_en"
    },
    {
      "text": "Harley's Humongous Adventure (化学者ハリーの波乱万丈, Kagakusha Harley no Haran Banjō) est un jeu vidéo d'action développé par Visual Concepts et sorti en 1993 sur Super Nintendo.",
